1931;;Don't Bet on Women;;American;;William K. Howard;;Jeanette MacDonald, Edmund Lowe, Roland Young;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Don%27t_Bet_on_Women;;On a whim, Herbert Blake proposes a wager with Roger Fallon that he won't be able to get a kiss during the coming 48 hours from the next woman who happens to walk into the room. Fallon takes the bet, whereupon the woman who turns up is Herbert's wife.